"title": "7315: blood, as basis of life",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7315",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture treats blood as the basis of life, and regards the shedding of blood as representing the end of life.</p>\n<h2>Blood symbolises life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:10-Lev17:14\">LEV 17:10–17:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:4-Gen9:6\">GEN 9:4–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:20-Deut12:25\">DEU 12:20–12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:15-2Sam23:17\">2SA 23:15–23:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:14\">PSA 72:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:34\">JER 2:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:1-Ezek33:6\">EZK 33:1–33:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:3-Matt27:4\">MAT 27:3–27:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:50-Luke11:51\">LUK 11:50–11:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:35-Matt23:36\">MAT 23:35–23:36</a></p>\n<h2>Blood indicating violent death</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8-Gen4:11\">GEN 4:8–4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">GEN 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:22-Judg9:24\">JDG 9:22–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:5-1Kgs2:6\">1KI 2:5–2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:28-1Kgs2:34\">1KI 2:28–2:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:30-2Kgs9:33\">2KI 9:30–9:33</a></p>\n<h2>Shedding blood as a sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:13\">EXO 20:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:17\">DEU 5:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:21-Gen42:22\">GEN 42:21–42:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:1-Deut21:9\">DEU 21:1–21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:16\">2KI 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10-Prov1:19\">PRO 1:10–1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:21\">ISA 26:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:18-Matt15:19\">MAT 15:18–15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:20-Mark7:21\">MRK 7:20–7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:28-Rom1:29\">ROM 1:28–1:29</a></p>\n<h2>The eating of blood forbidden</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev3:17\">LEV 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:26-Lev7:27\">LEV 7:26–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:10-Lev17:14\">LEV 17:10–17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:23\">DEU 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:31-1Sam14:34\">1SA 14:31–14:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:19-Acts15:20\">ACT 15:19–15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:29\">ACT 15:29</a></p>",
